import React from 'react'

import { AppIconContainer } from './AppIconContainer'


export const AppChevron = () => (
  <AppLocationIcon
    width="12"
    height="12"
    viewBox="0 0 12 15"
    fill="none"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"
  >
    <path d="M0.5 0.5L4.5 5.5L8.5 0.5" stroke="#3C3E3F" strokeLinecap="round"/>
  </AppLocationIcon>
)
